00:05:59,200 --> 00:06:02,410
"MASHIRAO OJIRO. SIFAT, EKOR"
Dalam saat genting, Ida jadi orang utama.

117
00:06:02,410 --> 00:06:03,410
"TENYA IDA. SIFAT, ENJIN"
Sebelum itu,

118
00:06:03,410 --> 00:06:06,540
