rasa saya tak patut sertainya.

159
00:08:19,330 --> 00:08:21,450
ITSUKA KENDO. SIFAT, PENUMBUK GERGASI

160
00:08:21,450 --> 00:08:24,620
Kita rakam iklan bersama
semasa latihan industri.

161
00:08:24,620 --> 00:08:28,660
Jadi, kita seolah-olah
dah terikat bersama.

162
00:08:28,660 --> 00:08:31,500
Kita ibarat kesukaan.

163
00:08:31,500 --> 00:08:33,250
Kesukaan?

164
00:08:34,500 --> 00:08:35,950
Maksudnya

165
