188
00:09:46,410 --> 00:09:48,160
Berusaha, pasukan Kendo!

189
00:09:48,160 --> 00:09:50,160
Pusingan dua, mula!

190
00:09:50,160 --> 00:09:52,120
"BANTAH SIARAN BERAT SEBELAH"
Berhenti bersikap berat sebelah!

191
00:09:52,120 --> 00:09:53,790
Jangan begitu.

192
00:09:54,120 --> 00:09:56,250
Okey, serang.

193
00:09:56,250 --> 00:09:57,620
Baik!

194
00:09:58,500 --> 00:10:01,950
Apakah posisi Kendo dalam kelas B?

195
00:10:01,950 --> 00:10:03,700
Kendo? Dia sangat hebat.

196
00:10:03,700 --> 00:10:05,330
Suara awak sangat kuat.

197
00:10:05,330 --> 00:10:07,620
"TETSUTETSU TETSUTETSU. SIFAT, KELULI"
Dia ialah ketua kelas kami.

198
00:10:07,620 --> 00:10:11,200
Dia sangat pintar dan
boleh buat penilaian dengan tenang.

199
00:10:11,200 --> 00:10:14,790
Dia juga berani menolong
dalam saat genting.

200
00:10:14,790 --> 00:10:18,160
Dia juga sangat ceria.

201
00:10:18,160 --> 00:10:19,080
Tanpa dia,

202
00:10:19,080 --> 00:10:22,250
semua pelajar kelas B
pasti telah dihasut Monoma.

203
00:10:22,250 --> 00:10:23,830
Kenapa cakap begitu?

204
00:10:23,830 --> 00:10:25,290
Dia ketua dalam kelas B.

205
00:10:25,290 --> 00:10:28,750
Dialah perempuan itu, Itsuka Kendo!

206
